		<title>Teen Hackers Take Over Google</title>
		<link>http://dharmafly.com/youngrewiredstate</link>
		<comments>http://dharmafly.com/youngrewiredstate#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 26 Aug 2009 12:01:24 +0000</pubDate>
